    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>准备好体验下一代卡车模拟游戏。</strong></h2>驾驶重达数吨的卡车，横跨澳大利亚，驶过一段又一段道路，你将看到风景如画的滨海公路，也会遇到坎坷难行的泥土路。尽赏这片壮美大陆的每一个日出和日落。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1327040/extras/d985ae6cd6a1d29daa9465c8535b07be.poster.avif?t=1770128108\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1327040/extras/d985ae6cd6a1d29daa9465c8535b07be.webm?t=1770128108\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1327040/extras/d985ae6cd6a1d29daa9465c8535b07be.mp4?t=1770128108\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>感受卡车驾驶舱外的自由！</strong></h2>现在可以走出驾驶舱，亲手固定牵引挂钩，还能检查和调整货物的堆垛。手动加油，亲自将油枪插入油箱。游戏的方方面面都能让你体验真正的逼真和自由！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1327040/extras/aca3233c31216079df5c7d7473953fbb.poster.avif?t=1770128108\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1327040/extras/aca3233c31216079df5c7d7473953fbb.webm?t=1770128108\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1327040/extras/aca3233c31216079df5c7d7473953fbb.mp4?t=1770128108\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>货物 - 不只是一节车厢</strong></h2>发现各类挂车，各有各的装载机制。亲手给挂车和半挂车装货，亲手给油罐充装。时刻注意：货物的摆放位置与方式以及实际重量都会影响卡车的操控。务必考虑车辆的性能与路况，谨慎规划车辆负荷。还有，别忘了，我们是在澳大利亚，这里多挂公路列车的发源地。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1327040/extras/6b642e5ca3dd0b99b15ee53273ff8025.poster.avif?t=1770128108\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1327040/extras/6b642e5ca3dd0b99b15ee53273ff8025.webm?t=1770128108\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1327040/extras/6b642e5ca3dd0b99b15ee53273ff8025.mp4?t=1770128108\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>澳大利亚/<strong>[/h2]<br>全心感受澳大利亚独特的自然风光和多样性。感受沥青道路以及崎岖坎坷的土路和石子路。国土广阔，你可以自由探索、寻找最佳货运路线。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1327040/extras/6648e0942b2d9407da44b1dd138ba1f4.poster.avif?t=1770128108\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1327040/extras/6648e0942b2d9407da44b1dd138ba1f4.webm?t=1770128108\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1327040/extras/6648e0942b2d9407da44b1dd138ba1f4.mp4?t=1770128108\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> 动态天气条件和昼夜循环 </strong></h2>体验天气条件对卡车操控的真实影响。雨雪和大雾需要你额外专注，每一次跑车也因此而遇到各不相同的难题和挑战。一边驾驶重型卡车，一边欣赏日出和日落的壮丽景致，看着白天和黑夜丝滑过渡，让你的行车更添几分真实和感觉。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1327040/extras/e2351423521a45423827335623c8acf1.poster.avif?t=1770128108\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1327040/extras/e2351423521a45423827335623c8acf1.webm?t=1770128108\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1327040/extras/e2351423521a45423827335623c8acf1.mp4?t=1770128108\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>更多特色： </strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>运输货物，前往澳大利亚各地。<br></li><li>互动驾驶舱，舱内主要的控制装置现在全部可以互动。<br>[*主动参与道路事件。<br></li><li>不用退出界面，平板就可以管理订单和公司。<br></li><li>先进的半挂车装载系统，手动摆放货物。<br></li><li>在线合作模式可供最多4名玩家一同完成订单。<br></li><li>不论是旧车型，还是现代的18轮怪物，各种卡车一应俱全。<br></li><li>卡车可以解锁、升级，也可以改装。<br></li><li>路况真实。<br></li><li>多种道路事件：事故、道路施工、自然现象。<br></li><li>可以与警察互动，也有可能遭受罚款。<br></li><li>培养你的角色，获得不同货物的运输许可。<br></li><li>支持游戏方向盘</li></ul></strong></strong></h2>",
